
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>KPI邮件通知</title>

<style>
	html {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: #eee;
	}
	.wrap {
		width: 600px;
		height: auto;
		margin: 20px auto;
		padding: 10px 20px;
		background: #fff;
		border-radius: 10px;
		border:1px solid #e6b02c;
	}
	p, a {
		font-family: Helvetica, Arial, "Microsoft Yahei", "SimSun", sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="wrap">
		<p><strong>Hi,${username}</strong><br/><br/></p>
		<p>${message}：</p>
		<a href="${linkhref}">${linkhref}</a>
		<p style="color:#ccc; font-size: 12px;">(如果您无法点击此链接，请将它复制到浏览器地址栏后按Enter键访问)</p>
		<p>为了保证您的帐号安全，该链接24小时内有效，点击一次后失效。</p>
		<p style="text-align: right;"><br/>谢谢<br />KPI运营团队</p>
	</div>

</body>
</html>